    "seo": {
      "title": "MRI Brain CSF Flow Study at Cadabams Diagnostics | 3T Scan",
      "description": "Understand your brain’s fluid dynamics with a painless, 30-minute MRI Brain CSF Flow Study at Cadabams Diagnostics. No radiation, same-day slots available.\n",
